articles.title: Number of cheetah deaths at Kuno National Park not low, says Supreme Court - The Indian Express
articles.description: As of now, six adult cheetahs — all relocated from Namibia and South Africa — and three cubs born in India have died since March this year at Madhya Pradesh's Kuno National Park.
articles.content:
The Supreme Court on Monday remarked that the number of deaths of African cheetahs at Madhya Pradesh’s Kuno National Park (KNP) was not low.
